## Key Commands to Remember

```bash
# Extract PDF metadata
pdfinfo file.pdf

# Extract image EXIF data
exiftool image.jpg

# Install tools if needed
sudo apt install poppler-utils          # for pdfinfo
sudo apt install libimage-exiftool-perl # for exiftool
```

