## What EXIF Data Can Reveal

| EXIF Field | What it reveals |
|------------|----------------|
| Camera Model | Device used to take photo |
| GPS Position | Exact location photo was taken |
| Date/Time | When photo was taken |
| Software | Editing software used |
| Serial Number | Unique camera identifier |

